是建立海堤的特別方法。他解釋，會在約100平方米的海面內，擺放55個扭工字塊，扭工字塊會一個貼一個地擺放。"},{"pid":"671ca95b952d69397a13c66a215dd62ee9dd27de","tid":622581,"uid":188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"喂 工程師 你而家得一忽跟到設計<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多位 放整齊 放錯左阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d281efd84c56ce71b6917e4f4b8cf31fc94c10ea","tid":622581,"uid":25028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"總之就冇事啦 唔好質疑支那建築<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0be2570b65577574205532e4d4324bdbea66187","tid":622581,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"「總之無問題啦，你地班友識舊石咩！」"},{"pid":"52cc8fb25e42a987a86a74f758f9421ccf387460","tid":622581,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"由得佢地啦，期待死人畫面出現"},{"pid":"f1191c4c00b3abc1afb5f6147012fbd507fdf3e6","tid":622581,"uid":46170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"指鹿為馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快啲黎次十號波<br />\n睇下佢哋仲有咩好解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2283d643604f8b15c52783a5e31413bfe378e5f9","tid":622581,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"671ca95b952d69397a13c66a215dd62ee9dd27de","tid":622581,"uid":188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"喂 工程師 你而家得一忽跟到設計<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多位 放整齊 放錯左阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla