/>\n<br />\n香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1e4d3475efe7d7faf65467c9c38ba135d5c93b","tid":622581,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"無問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最緊要之後你唔好汁番佢就得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3d0982a43cee9b5cb24b6262f85731dfda0844","tid":622581,"uid":38255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f05dceb4a00b8cded9a8e302d6b05eae3b45e169","tid":622581,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"路政署官員昨日到港珠澳大橋人工島，視察防波堤的情況，署長鍾錦華表示，防波堤設計<span style=\"color: red;\">具科學性、合理性和安全性，沒有出現被沖散的情況</span>。 路政署首席政府工程師江大榮說，防波堤用了同一種扭工字塊，但在兩個不同地點、不同位置，有不同功能。他說，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公眾可能誤解</span></span>，以為防波堤受不住沖擊散落，<span style=\"color: red;\">但事實並非如此</span>。 他說，一般會用100年一遇的水位作標準，但在西人工島的位置，選用300年一遇的水位，預計水位可高達9.5米。 江大榮又說，隨機安放防波堤在本港或美國的海岸保護工程，有用這個名詞，<span style=\"color: red;\">有特定用意</span>，是建立海堤的特別方法。他解釋，會在約100平方米的海面內，擺放55個扭工字塊，扭工字塊會一個貼一個地擺放。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"係有隨機安放，但唔係好似而家咁求基放叫隨機安放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n借隔黎post巴打圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/175946_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F175946_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff35184e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://pix.avaxnews.com/avaxnews/0b/fb/0000fb0b_medium.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpix.avaxnews.com%2Favaxnews%2F0b%2Ffb%2F0000fb0b_medium.jpeg&h=ec4ca8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wimp.com/images/sthumbs/2015/09/6ac6722d90283fe4587751e97d653b21_bridge6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wimp.com%2Fimages%2Fsthumbs%2F2015%2F09%2F6ac6722d90283fe4587751e97d653b21_bridge6.jpg&h=b453183a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://data.oresundsbron.com/cms/inline-images/15084183-_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.oresundsbron.com%2Fcms%2Finline-images%2F15084183-_0.jpg&h=3847ff70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vbbound.com/sites/default/files/listings/chesapeake-bay-bridge-tunnel-04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vbbound.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Flistings%2Fchesapeake-bay-bridge-tunnel-04.jpg&h=d56f2340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dprbcn.files.wordpress.com/2011/09/umihotaru1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdprbcn.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F09%2Fumihotaru1.jpg&h=6002fc38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/180908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F180908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=672ff088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不如局方畀幅外國都係港豬噢咁既樣既相出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205dd9509d2335e699c396f5e729b2f5da4fd0b3","tid":622581,"uid":30830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:11:31.000Z","msg":"呢個 Post 有無相關專家出嚟講講<br />\n自己做醫生知道有啲嘢外人睇同內行睇係兩回事<br />\n但呢個政府真係 &hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"4cde82b47f9e2936b42ac3020a9940c195384a29","tid":622581,"uid":14240,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"Concrete armour units may be placed <span style=\"color: red;\">randomly or in a regular pattern</span>, ..., while the <span style=\"color: red;\">more complex units depend upon the interlocking between units to<br />\nachieve the hydraulic stability</span>. True random placing is difficult to achieve, and inevitably<br />\nresults in some units not being as well interlocked as others. Although placing to a<br />\npredetermined layout is usually specified for interlocking units, this is also difficult to<br />\nachieve except under favourable conditions of good underwater visibility and calm seas.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed1f6c8857ea5bd80a8fe8e6e5ae6d8c678ef14","tid":622581,"uid":14240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4cde82b47f9e2936b42ac3020a9940c195384a29","tid":622581,"uid":14240,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"Concrete armour units may be placed <span style=\"color: red;\">randomly or in a regular pattern</span>, ..., while the <span style=\"color: red;\">more complex units depend upon the interlocking between units to<br />\nachieve the hydraulic stability</span>. True random placing is difficult to achieve, and inevitably<br />\nresults in some units not being as well interlocked as others. Although placing to a<br />\npredetermined layout is usually specified for interlocking units, this is also difficult to<br />\nachieve except under favourable conditions of good underwater visibility and calm seas.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"from Port Work Design Manual <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cedd.gov.hk/eng/publications/ceo/doc/p4_txt.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cedd.gov.hk%2Feng%2Fpublications%2Fceo%2Fdoc%2Fp4_txt.pdf&d=sj%2Bd%2B6mvMlltIgHifkvVM%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=93f68952\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cedd.gov.hk/eng/publications/ceo/doc/p4_txt.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ed3d2062de7d096c96a43a9eaaf2714b3bae1e2f","tid":622581,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201